title: Orbit Earth's Extraordinary Journey E01
description:
<a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00xztbr" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00xztbr</a>

Right now you're hurtling around the Sun at 100,000 kms an hour. 
 Join Kate Humble and Dr Helen Czerski as they explore the relationship between the Earth's orbit and the weather.

Episode 1:

 1/3 Following the Earth's orbit from July to the December solstice.
